[2] Minnesota
Date: Sat 6 Jan 2018
Source: Grand Rapids Herald-Review [edited]
http://www.grandrapidsmn.com/news/whooping-cough-cases-confirmed-at-local-schools/article_e59db2ec-f260-11e7-a742-6b79e92512b1.html


Several confirmed or probable cases of whooping cough have been reported in Itasca county. Statewide, the number is nearing 800, according to the Minnesota Department of Health statistics. On [Thu 4 Jan 2018], Independent School District 318 sent a message informing parents that a few confirmed cases have been identified in local schools.

[Byline: Britta Arendt]

